    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy for hemolysis (RH < 1 at all five operating points), hydraulic performance, and wall shear stress distribution. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
